title: 2 bedroom apartment #1 near JFK station
posting_body: ['Currently available: Apartment #1;\xa0 1150 square foot unit', 'Rent: $2,500/ month paid monthly', '- Recently renovated including fully insulated walls & ceilings', '- 2 spacious bedrooms', '- separate large living room & dining room (can be used as third bedroom)', '- eat in kitchen with gas stove and refrigerator', '- pantry with sink, storage cabinets and shelves', '- 1 bathroom with large claw-footed tub and shower', '- Utilities: Water included (Tenant pays gas heat, electricity and internet)', '-NO PETS ALLOWED', 'Unit has its own back porch, oak floors throughout, shared\xa0 washing machine in cellar, street parking, one block to JFK station with access to Downtown Boston, restaurants/bars and grocery stores located nearby, walking distance to Carson Beach, no smoking allowed, no students.', '12 month lease required, first and last month rent required.', 'No broker fees', 'All Applicants will be evaluated based on Financial Eligibility, Previous Rental History, and Credit Worthiness.']
